    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "So I added a geo-search recipe to show how you can update search parameters and synchronize the URL. I also updated the search parameters guide. \r\n\r\nThis geo search example is very basic and only feature:\r\n\r\n* a regular search through the searchbox. \r\n* a map that when we click somewhere perform a new search. \r\n\r\nWe still need to do #1860 because with this example:\r\n\r\n* the search is not triggered when moving the map. (mostly because I didn't find a `dragEnd` event with the lib used at the moment). \r\n* No autocomplete. ",
